🐍 ANACONDA – Official Trailer (2025) | Action Comedy in 4K
Expect the unexpected. Anaconda brings the heat (and the hiss) in this wild action-comedy pairing of Jack Black & Paul Rudd. Big laughs, bigger snakes, and chaos on every scale.

Film Overview
When Paul Rudd’s wildlife documentarian and Jack Black’s overconfident adventurer set out to film the legendary “King Anaconda” in the Amazon, things go sideways fast. Every trap fails, every creature lurks, and what was meant to be a story turns into a full-on survival comedy where the jungle is as dangerous as the snake.
